commit.message:
Merge pull request #4 from sonntagd/feature/fix_pod_link

fix pod link
Require a specific version of Types::Standard

Release v0.150900

Wherever I did the last CPAN release from, I didn't push it back
up to git and tag it. Fix that now.

Don't strip whitespace chars from the end of the hash in PBKDF2_hex

Oops! unpack "A*" removes spaces and newlines from the end of the string
it unpacks, so they were getting omitted from the hex output.

Fixes CPAN RT#102447.
Add tests to validate that the various hash formats come out to the right length

Add a new option to limit password length

This prevents algorithmic complexity attacks like
https://www.djangoproject.com/weblog/2013/sep/15/security/

Thanks to Gabor Szabo for reporting.
Add HMACSHA3 hash, supporting SHA3-224 through 512.
